      "author": "nguyenvanduocit",
      "description": "## 🐛 Bug Fixes\n\n### Improved Bot Detection Bypass\n- **Add default Chrome user agent**: Webview now uses a real Chrome user agent by default\n  - Electron's default user agent contains \"Electron\" which triggers bot detection\n  - Now defaults to `Chrome/131.0.0.0` user agent when none is specified\n  - Users can still override with custom user agent in gate settings\n\nThis is a follow-up to v1.11.12 for better Cloudflare compatibility.\n\n## 📦 Installation\n\nUpdate through Obsidian Community Plugins or download manually.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nguyenvanduocit/obsidian-open-gate/compare/1.11.12...1.11.13",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.11.13: Add default Chrome user agent",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-17T01:12:18Z",
      "tag": "1.11.13"
    },
