          "size": 487
        }
      ],
      "author": "nguyenvanduocit",
      "description": "## 🐛 Bug Fixes\n\n### Cloudflare Verification Fix\n- **Fix \"Verifying you are human\" never completing**: Removed webview attributes that triggered bot detection\n  - Removed `disablewebsecurity` attribute that was flagging the browser as automated\n  - Removed invalid `crossorigin` attribute (not supported by Electron webview)\n  - Webview now behaves like a standard browser, passing Cloudflare and other anti-bot checks\n\nFixes #87\n\n## 📦 Installation\n\nUpdate through Obsidian Community Plugins or download manually.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nguyenvanduocit/obsidian-open-gate/compare/1.11.11...1.11.12",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.11.12: Fix Cloudflare human verification detection",
